name: Swap Meet
wikiSummary: A "white trash" love song of sorts and one of the album's poppier moments.  Ostensily about a poverty stricken couple's shared passions.  The chorus refers to Cobain's own relationship with at-the-time-girlfriend Tracy Marander.
wikiText:
A "white trash" love song of sorts and one of the album's poppier moments.  Ostensily about a poverty stricken couple's shared passions.  The chorus refers to Cobain's own relationship with at-the-time-girlfriend Tracy Marander.
